          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话虽如此，只是那张良诡计多端，韩信广有韬略。只怕难以取胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾身备得有酒，请大王畅饮几杯，以解愁烦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍！"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有孤王在帐中心神不定，\n想起了当年事好不伤心。\n有淮阴小韩信用兵如神。\n孤一身怎能杀冒敌充锋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内喊声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "又听得一阵阵金鼓齐鸣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（军官上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "军官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王：韩信带领十万之众将垓下团团围住了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（军官下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听一言来怒气生，\n骂声韩信休逞能！"
        },
        {
          "character": "人来带过乌骓马、虞姬",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大王息怒且稍停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "人来带过乌骓马、虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀大王：看夜深了，倘若那贼暗地埋伏，岂不中了他的诡计？况且大王饮酒\n带醉，今晚暂息一宵，明日再与他鏖战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "美人言之有理，待等天明定要与那厮决一死战！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内喊声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得有人声震，\n四面里皆是楚歌声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听四面皆是楚歌之声，想是吾营中兵将作歌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（军官上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "军官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王：大事不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事惊惶？"
        },
        {
          "character": "军官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉营中的兵将，俱作楚人之歌。我营中士兵闻之个个思乡，军心要变了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "竟有这等之事！速速到各营安抚他们！快去快去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "军官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（军官下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉军吹箫作楚声，竟来扰乱我军心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫美人搀扶孤后帐进，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吐） 呜噜噜噜……"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕只怕西楚难保存！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（项羽、虞姬同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "项羽→虞姬",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
