    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四将"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四将同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！吾等奉了韩元帅将令围困垓下，捉拿项羽，就此前往！\n请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四将同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "同白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "项羽 （内西皮导板） 盖世英雄遭围困，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（项羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "四面俱是汉家兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、四将同上，同围项羽。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人马呐喊金鼓鸣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四将起打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "层层人马杀气腾。\n孤一人能挡百万军！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四将 （同西皮摇板） 来在阵前把话论，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫声项羽听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少若迟延命难存！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来怒气生，\n胆大小儿休逞能！\n猛虎岂怕羊一群！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（项羽起打，项羽下。众人同追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 4
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "内侍",
        "愿借大王青锋剑",
        "楚歌吹散我八千队",
        "老天不把人意遂",
        "虞姬",
        "项羽"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虞姬上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "晓妆梳洗乌云挽，\n玉容寂寞泪涟涟。\n满腹愁肠锁眉尖。\n中奸计被困在九里山。\n锦绣基业难保全。\n想必是大王爷转回营盘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（项羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天意亡楚欲兴汉，\n盖世功劳付流泉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王回来了！今日与汉兵交战胜负如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "力拔山兮气盖世，时不利兮骓不逝。骓不逝兮怎奈何，虞兮虞兮奈若何！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，大王为何发此长叹？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "美人呐，想孤家自出兵以来，今已五载七十余战，未常有败；今日被困在垓下，\n此乃是天亡楚也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤家用兵勇无对，\n百战百胜逞雄威。\n九里山前被贼围。\n眼见得霸业竟成灰！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老天不把人意遂、楚歌吹散我八千队、虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王吓，这："
        },
        {
          "character": "老天不把人意遂、楚歌吹散我八千队、虞姬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉兵将吾困，四下楚歌声，大王意气尽，贱妾怎聊生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老天不把人意遂、楚歌吹散我八千队、虞姬",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大王休要把锐气败，\n还须早早作安排。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老天不把人意遂、楚歌吹散我八千队、虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王还要早作良图，杀出重围，恢复霸业才是正理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳吓，美人呐，那汉兵虽有百万之众，何足惧哉！只是行军之际，交锋对垒，\n怎能带得你行走？也罢，闻得汉王乃好色之徒。你可以前去伏侍于他去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王说哪里话来？自古道：忠臣不事二主，烈女不嫁二夫。大王欲图天下大事，\n岂可以妾身为累？贱妾情愿尽节以报大王宠爱之恩便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古常言道得好：\n烈女不侍二夫男。\n情愿尽节在君前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "愿借大王青锋剑、项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "愿借大王青锋剑、项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "虞姬果肯身殉难，\n到叫孤家心痛酸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "愿借大王青锋剑、项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀美人，你果有此心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果有此心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实有此意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实有此意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢罢罢，我项羽纵死九泉也得瞑目！但是一件……"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是你我恩爱一场，叫孤家怎能舍得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王力图霸业，前程万里；妾身一命，轻如鸿毛。望大王勿以妾身为念！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是孤家实实难舍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大王他把妾身恋，\n难舍难分泪涟涟。\n顷刻一命染黄泉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虞姬自刎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "美人呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见虞姬寻短见，\n好叫孤家痛伤惨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虞美人呐！"
        },
