      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（渔夫撑船上。项羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "弃甲曳兵出危险，\n又只见江边一舟船。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那厢来的敢么是项王千岁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？怎么认得孤家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉那年曾在千岁营中送过粮草，因此认得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王为何这等狼狈？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤与汉兵交战，被他等杀得大败逃避至此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，千岁请上船来，待老汉渡千岁过江如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想吾项羽，威名四海，无人不知；今日兵败至此，有何面目去见江东父老？也\n罢！待我自刎乌江，以谢天下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁请上船来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四将同追上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀，汉兵到了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（渔夫急下，项羽自刎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看项羽自刎，吾等将他首级割下献于韩元帅便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四将同割首级，项羽下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。四将同下。）"
        }
      ],
